OL,3,C'Conservation milestone' as four
OL,4,Cendangered tigers born at animal park
OL,6,FAn animal park is marking a
OL,7,F"conservation milestone" following the
OL,8,Fbirth of four tiger cubs from a
OL,9,Fcritically endangered species.
OL,11,FThe Sumatran tiger cubs were the first
OL,12,Fever to be born at Howletts Wild
OL,13,FAnimal Park, near Canterbury in Kent,
OL,14,Fon April 9.
OL,16,FThe park is hailing their birth as a
OL,17,Fsignificant boost for the future of
OL,18,FSumatran tigers, with less than 400
OL,19,Fremaining in the wild.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@XO]
