OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779274977
OL,3,C'Conservation milestone' as four
OL,4,Cendangered tigers born at animal park
OL,6,FKeepers have described the cubs as
OL,7,F"healthy, fluffy and growing well".
OL,9,FA Howletts spokesperson said: "This is
OL,10,Fa hugely significant moment for
OL,11,FHowletts and for the conservation of
OL,12,Fthis extraordinary species.
OL,14,F"The birth of four healthy Sumatran
OL,15,Ftiger cubs is fantastic news, and we
OL,16,Fare thrilled to be able to share this
OL,17,Fspecial milestone with our visitors
OL,18,Fduring Springfest this half-term."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@bO]qD@_OUvD@AOUzD@bO]
