OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779274977
OL,3,C'Conservation milestone' as four
OL,4,Cendangered tigers born at animal park
OL,6,FThe cubs' mother, Tipah, born in
OL,7,FJanuary 2019, arrived at the park in
OL,8,FMay 2022 and these are her first cubs.
OL,9,FThey are believed to be one of the
OL,10,Flargest litters recorded to have been
OL,11,Fproduced for Sumatran tigers.
OL,13,FFather Nakal was born in February 2014
OL,14,Fand joined the park in July 2025.
